      </li>
      <li class="list-group-item">
        5. cut onion and tomatoes into small squares
      </li>
      <li class="list-group-item">
        6. when jalapenos are cooked take them out and add more oil and onions
      </li>
      <li class="list-group-item">
        7. after a few minutes add in 1 tsp of garlic and the tomatoes
      </li>
      <li class="list-group-item">
        8. mix and let it cook on low-medium heat
      </li>
      <li class="list-group-item">
        9. cut steak pieces into thin strips or squares and season with salt and pepper
      </li>
      <li class="list-group-item">
        10. add oil to a new pan and cook the steak pieces
      </li>
      <li class="list-group-item">
        11. combine verythign together and add in 2 large spoons of red seasoning
      </li>
